      },
      {
        "id": "block-091",
        "kind": "paragraph",
        "order": 91,
        "text": "图3-1-16 网络测试"
      },
      {
        "id": "block-092",
        "kind": "paragraph",
        "order": 92,
        "text": "五．信令分析：进行log测试数据分析，发现网络问题，提出解决方案，如图3-1-17，3-1-18."
      },
      {
        "id": "block-093",
        "kind": "paragraph",
        "order": 93,
        "mediaRefs": [
          "rId118"
        ]
      },
      {
        "id": "block-094",
        "kind": "paragraph",
        "order": 94,
        "text": "图3-1-17 信令分析"
      },
      {
        "id": "block-095",
        "kind": "paragraph",
        "order": 95,
        "mediaRefs": [
          "rId119"
        ]
      },
      {
        "id": "block-096",
        "kind": "paragraph",
        "order": 96,
        "text": "图3-1-18 问题分析"
      },
      {
        "id": "block-097",
        "kind": "paragraph",
        "order": 97,
        "text": "六．端到端优化：进行端到端数据配置，参数调整提升网络KPI。"
      },
      {
        "id": "block-098",
        "kind": "paragraph",
        "order": 98,
        "text": "（一）优化前性能指标提取"
      },
      {
        "id": "block-099",
        "kind": "paragraph",
        "order": 99,
        "text": "方法1："
      },
      {
        "id": "block-100",
        "kind": "paragraph",
        "order": 100,
        "text": "（1）在端到端优化任务，点击数据中心，如图3-1-19"
      },
      {
        "id": "block-101",
        "kind": "paragraph",
        "order": 101,
        "mediaRefs": [
          "rId120"
        ]
      },
      {
        "id": "block-102",
        "kind": "paragraph",
        "order": 102,
        "text": "图3-1-19 性能指标提取"
      },
      {
        "id": "block-103",
        "kind": "paragraph",
        "order": 103,
        "text": "（2）根据指标选取相应的模块（比如：无线侧）,如图3-1-20"
      },
      {
        "id": "block-104",
        "kind": "paragraph",
        "order": 104,
        "mediaRefs": [
          "rId121"
        ]
      },
      {
        "id": "block-105",
        "kind": "paragraph",
        "order": 105,
        "text": "图3-1-20 模块选取"
      },
      {
        "id": "block-106",
        "kind": "paragraph",
        "order": 106,
        "text": "（3）左侧导航栏选取性能，右侧界面选取查看的站点名称，指标名称以及时间段，如图3-1-21"
      },
      {
        "id": "block-107",
        "kind": "paragraph",
        "order": 107,
        "mediaRefs": [
          "rId122"
        ]
      },
      {
        "id": "block-108",
        "kind": "paragraph",
        "order": 108,
        "text": "图3-1-21 性能指标查询"
      },
      {
        "id": "block-109",
        "kind": "paragraph",
        "order": 109,
        "text": "方法2："
      },
      {
        "id": "block-110",
        "kind": "paragraph",
        "order": 110,
        "text": "（1）根据指定站点进入（比如：站点1），如图3-1-22"
      },
      {
        "id": "block-111",
        "kind": "paragraph",
        "order": 111,
        "mediaRefs": [
          "rId123"
        ]
      },
      {
        "id": "block-112",
        "kind": "paragraph",
        "order": 112,
        "text": "图3-1-22 指定站点"
      },
      {
        "id": "block-113",
        "kind": "paragraph",
        "order": 113,
        "text": "（2） 选择不同问题，显示相应的实时性能指标，如图3-1-23"
      },
      {
        "id": "block-114",
        "kind": "paragraph",
        "order": 114,
        "mediaRefs": [
          "rId124"
        ]
      },
      {
        "id": "block-115",
        "kind": "paragraph",
        "order": 115,
        "text": "图3-1-23 指定站点实时性能指标"
      },
      {
        "id": "block-116",
        "kind": "paragraph",
        "order": 116,
        "text": "（二）参数调整，包括配置参数和邻区参数调整，如图3-1-24"
      },
      {
        "id": "block-117",
        "kind": "paragraph",
        "order": 117,
        "mediaRefs": [
          "rId125"
        ]
      },
      {
        "id": "block-118",
        "kind": "paragraph",
        "order": 118,
        "text": "图3-1-24 参数调整"
      },
      {
        "id": "block-119",
        "kind": "paragraph",
        "order": 119,
        "text": "六．全网性能提升：通过全网配置参数的调整提升全网性能。"
      },
      {
        "id": "block-120",
        "kind": "paragraph",
        "order": 120,
        "text": "（一）优化前全网性能指标提取"
      },
      {
        "id": "block-121",
        "kind": "paragraph",
        "order": 121,
        "text": "1.选取“全网性能提升”然后单击进入“数据中心”，如图3-1-25"
      },
      {
        "id": "block-122",
        "kind": "paragraph",
        "order": 122,
        "mediaRefs": [
          "rId126"
        ]
      },
      {
        "id": "block-123",
        "kind": "paragraph",
        "order": 123,
        "text": "图3-1-25 全网性能指标提取"
      },
      {
        "id": "block-124",
        "kind": "paragraph",
        "order": 124,
        "text": "2.选取时间段和指标类型，如图3-1-26"
      },
      {
        "id": "block-125",
        "kind": "paragraph",
        "order": 125,
        "mediaRefs": [
          "rId127"
        ]
      },
      {
        "id": "block-126",
        "kind": "paragraph",
        "order": 126,
        "text": "图3-1-26 全网性能指标"
      },
      {
        "id": "block-127",
        "kind": "paragraph",
        "order": 127,
        "text": "（二）相关参数调整，如图3-1-27"
      },
      {
        "id": "block-128",
        "kind": "paragraph",
        "order": 128,
        "text": "在导航栏选取“配置”，选取相关站点，在右侧界面设置小区和邻区参数"
      },
      {
        "id": "block-129",
        "kind": "paragraph",
        "order": 129,
        "mediaRefs": [
          "rId128"
        ]
      },
      {
        "id": "block-130",
        "kind": "paragraph",
        "order": 130,
        "text": "图3-1-27 参数调整"
      },
      {
        "id": "block-131",
        "kind": "paragraph",
        "order": 131,
        "text": "随堂测试"
      },
      {
        "id": "block-132",
        "kind": "paragraph",
        "order": 132,
        "text": "通过仿真软件完成指定站点室内信息提取。"
      },
      {
        "id": "block-133",
        "kind": "paragraph",
        "order": 133,
        "text": "通过仿真软件完成指定站点室外信息提取。"
      },
      {
        "id": "block-134",
        "kind": "paragraph",
        "order": 134,
        "text": "请将答案截屏后，用手机拍照发给老师。"
